_:N1e25f9e405e24338b0e2ba09789841d1 <http://schema.org/name> "Simon Chesterman OBE, QPM" .
_:N1e25f9e405e24338b0e2ba09789841d1 <http://schema.org/image> <https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/694528962f0261139350892c/s465_Simon-Chesterman-Web.jpg> .
_:N1e25f9e405e24338b0e2ba09789841d1 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Simon Chesterman joined the Civil Nuclear Constabulary in January 2014 as the <abbr title=\"Civil Nuclear Constabulary\">CNC</abbr>’s deputy chief constable and was promoted to chief constable on 1 April 2019. \nHe is also the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.npcc.police.uk/\">National Police Chiefs’ Council</a> lead expert on armed policing. He began his career with <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.thamesvalley.police.uk\">Thames Valley Police</a> and went on to become deputy chief constable, specialist operations, <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.westmercia.police.uk\">West Mercia Police</a>. In 2012 he was awarded the Queen’s Police Medal.</p>\n" .
<https://www.gov.uk/> <http://schema.org/name> "Home" .
